                                     <a href="http://www.gracepointonline.org/pages/contact/">Report A Problem</a> 
                                     <br>Gracepoint â€“ Berkeley 1275 Harbor Bay Parkway Alameda, CA 94502</p>
      </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
